{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "76b78f17-5aa2-4f82-8614-083699e4da99",
    "name": "Gerhard's Office: 15 Vengeance",
    "sceneId": "eceae806-6f55-4cde-b517-c73b1c924fd9",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "23879dae-1d16-486d-8809-ce8912bd35de",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b918642b-0c56-4842-b98a-ad4dac7bf9d1",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Did you find something of interest about Herr Terk?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                    "sections": [
                        {
                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.hasActiveQuest",
                                "propId": "2fb29518-c7a8-4096-ac3c-36e50277242d",
                                "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                "questStatus": "0"
                            },
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                                    "id": "88175b20-94e0-4db6-a7de-fb17905a3b5b",
                                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                    "propId": "2fb29518-c7a8-4096-ac3c-36e50277242d",
                                    "target": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c0892478-cd25-4a16-a97b-48e52590f7c4",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "text": "I found this ledger book, sir, stashed away in a place of safety. I figured that if Terk thought it needed to be kept a secret, then there must be something interesting in it.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b089efe2-6845-405a-b49c-c01aa6358f53",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "That does sound intriguing... let me take a look at it, please.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "25f27d2d-21be-4f24-b825-1c63cd1062b4",
                    "propId": "a455851a-06a5-45a8-be4f-b1205302e816",
                    "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                    "change": "0",
                    "count": 1,
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.fade",
                    "scope": "FadeOut",
                    "fadeTime": "0.5",
                    "fadeTime2": 2,
                    "wait": true,
                    "fadeDown": 0.5,
                    "fadeColorR": 0,
                    "fadeColorG": 0,
                    "fadeColorB": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showVignette",
                    "vignetteName": "GerhardtReviewsLedgerColored.png",
                    "crossFadeTime": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.fade",
                    "scope": "FadeIn",
                    "fadeTime": "0.5",
                    "fadeTime2": "1",
                    "wait": true,
                    "fadeDown": 0.5,
                    "fadeColorR": 0,
                    "fadeColorG": 0,
                    "fadeColorB": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.wait",
                    "waitForSeconds": "2"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "59f79f56-bcfc-49f1-ad0d-435e9a99fdb5",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Ah, yes, this is very interesting... and useful.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "932a1b02-8336-4cfb-98d5-251a46a0b928",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "text": "What is it? It just looks like numbers to me.",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "de3ac2ba-dbcb-4ee9-a312-8726a3effa02",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "As I mentioned before, Herr Terk is methodical to the point of obsessive. He has entries in this book about receiving funds from someone he calls \"Patron\" regarding a certain \"SOC\". ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a4a03da6-f6e6-4b93-975a-4d85dfc6f530",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Tsk, tsk. It seems that Herr Terk has been bribed to spy upon me and upon you.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "11c21dc3-ed27-4286-bd75-06429687f60e",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3628a0a6-7d48-4a8c-9f6a-c216d34491dc",
                            "text": "Say Something Charming ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "b1a73378-71e6-438e-b5b3-6cc90951dc06",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "amount": "3",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "b14979be-8b01-4334-a8ea-124926092c55",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "85",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f73226a7-67ff-429f-b1bf-e352ee826b39",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "Terk has gone out of his way to be a jerk to everyone, but particularly Rogues. It's about time he learns that Rogues take care of their own.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "54ecea53-52b6-4e97-8f82-8baf58bab00d",
                            "text": "Say Something Clever ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "54e2a360-f372-4a81-87a3-710054d64dd5",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "So what are you planning to do with this evidence? You could use it to force Terk to act nicer to people and leave the Rogues alone.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2145a343-9cff-4940-9eef-9fa310399f68",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You have a point. Forcing Herr Terk to change his ways and act like a reasonable person toward others would be a roguish thing to do. On the other hand, even a polite Mortimer is an unpleasant Mortimer.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "23548d49-adf5-4d9c-ab11-0c8bf0ee160b",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You are more the aggrieved party here. Herr Terk has been exceptionally obnoxious towards you. What do you prefer Herr Terk's fate to be - fired from the school or forced to be nice to everyone?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "273cc716-923e-4cfd-8a5a-a08b6c6d8df8",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "4972008e-4cce-4883-b0af-bc1af07279d4",
                                            "text": "Fire Terk",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "47d6fd2f-558c-4775-a1e1-01b239ccae9f",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "I'd rather not see Terk again stalking the halls and giving everyone demerits again here at the University. He makes everyone's life miserable here.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "d3ed5c2b-5ceb-49f1-ae5b-c9b7d9ad56e6",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                                    "target": "85",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "c41b9844-4f45-40a6-8626-21d96f5dba92",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "amount": "2",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "06048f71-62fd-4b5a-a88d-533d10560b0c",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Very well, I will speak to the Headmaster soon about the matter of Herr Terk's resignation.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "fe2bd6a3-4079-4b45-bc7c-be1920afb429",
                                            "text": "Force Terk to be Polite",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "e9758998-ce5b-4ad1-954e-8ffde80f4b1b",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                                    "target": "85",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "299d1197-5ff0-4f20-872d-fc7068331299",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "amount": "3",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "649ed3b2-00cb-4517-9c32-e6a958e90416",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "text": "I think that it will be fitting punishment for Terk to have to be polite to everyone. He'll have to face every day doing something he hates.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": 0,
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "afb90cc7-f005-49e0-bd26-fc092b28cf98",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "A fitting fate indeed...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "7",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "137cc72f-31f9-4523-8a3c-8eab98b4a03a",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d6620b7c-d632-44bb-882d-a07c1e1296e7",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "So about this ledger... I thought one of our Rogue Rules was \"Thou Shalt not Steal from the School or other Classmates?\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b457b744-f907-497e-85fb-4b9f793efb43",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Oh, I fully intend to return this to Herr Terk... eventually. But not before I prove that he has accepted bribes, committed extortion, and reveal him to be the petty criminal that he is.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "a13eed70-87c5-4a56-8bdd-cfa01f242019",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "98",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "61009445-dc82-4d8b-9d95-40110f3755da",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b3bcecce-e669-454a-b8f9-af0bfd3564f5",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "So Terk the Jerk will soon be put out of our misery and out of work. Yes!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0e9dc203-cdfd-4515-88a0-64f6f631a072",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "You have done very well with this, Herr O'Conner. I will make the most of this ledger book.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                    "id": "239e9a06-0d84-4247-a581-6f8994a30791",
                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                    "propId": "43671d02-d7f6-441d-98cc-fbdeea33a771",
                    "target": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "954f178d-d3a7-45da-80dc-7eeb1a8698e7",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "text": "Does this mean that I'm an official Rogue now?",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "54e79b29-23d1-4dbe-b474-3d4208b2633d",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "amount": "5",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "85c1ca8a-6b94-47bf-9cf3-2ed4f04bb956",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "There is little doubt of that, Herr O'Conner.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f985fe07-ce83-4e4a-a653-81c57f67c2c4",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "We will speak more of this later. For now, auf Wiedersehen.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9e2b77a1-f9e0-4272-89e9-1fd76e2869c1",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "text": "Good day, sir.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.incrementTime",
                    "id": "098a17f5-c7e7-411b-a52a-63d89a37f1ff",
